{"tid":2190490,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★未列入標普500指數成份股 特斯拉盤後重挫6.4％","createTime":"2020-09-05T16:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T13:03:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c36ec8ca9a2081f20c86ef77643b978f0504a344","tid":2190490,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T16:51:45.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕負責美股標普500指數的委員會於當地時間4日盤後決定，將電商平台Etsy、電子測試設備（ATE）製造商泰瑞達（Teradyne）、生技公司Catalent等3間企業列入該指數成份股，並未如市場部份人士預期，將電動車廠特斯拉（Tesla）列入該指數中，使特斯拉盤後股價下挫6.4%。<br />\n<br />\n《CNBC》報導，此消息宣佈後，特斯拉盤後股價一度重挫一度重挫逾7%，因為日前特斯拉驚人的漲幅，除了其未來前景外，也是因為部份投資人預期，特斯拉本季將被列入標普500指數成份股所促成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3282596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3282596&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmRzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=d3ae9a1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3282596&h=ac9ae866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3282596</a>"},{"pid":"bd6316f23d823a38d9713364ef8c5942e97087bd","tid":2190490,"uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T16:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ZnCjdq.gif&amp;h=6c78f139&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"d7aff7e49f315037eef6f9dbba53769dbda58c5b","tid":2190490,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2054c0e785466142a3859a319029deeeebbcc7c3","tid":2190490,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b